OL,5, A strike by firefighters across        
OL,6, Scotland is "inevitable" unless an     
OL,7, improved pay offer is put on the table,
OL,8, a senior union official has warned.    
OL,10,FSince the summer members of the Fire   
OL,11,FBrigades Union (FBU) have rejected two 
OL,12,Fdeals worth 2% and 5%.                 
OL,14,FWith a strike ballot set to close next 
OL,15,Fmonth, the union said action could take
OL,16,Fplace as early as mid-February.        
OL,18,FThe Scottish government has said pay   
OL,19,Ffor firefighters is negotiated through 
OL,20,FUK-wide bargaining arrangements.       
